> "That's Autobot's nature"said the Predacon"Never leaves their own faction
> behind... They will fight till the end if was necesary, they fight for their
> own kind; We, most of we fight for Power or earn the Powerfull's favor; I
> personally get bored with pollitics so I remain quiet in my lab enjoying
> watching the intriges and watching others intrige, altough somethims is
> boring too... but If I were Autobot, I'd be more bored"

Rodimus nodded as Perceptor talked, "Yeah, the Autobots are really
stupid for doing that." Although even after he said it, it felt
strange to him. He shook his head as if to clear it as Perceptor
continued speaking.

> "Listen me, Rodimus"add the Predacon"dont do something that you'll regret
> later... Remember that she isnt in a inminet danger, she isnt a menace...
> but she will be in a real danger if you do something stupid"

Rodimus' optics harden, "I would never do anything to put her in
danger." he said, anger and some strange sort of guilt sweeping over
him for a moment. "I will not allow anyone to come to harm because of
my own failure!" he said as he clenched his fists held at his sides.
